data.description: Motivated Seller! This beautiful 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom single-family home is nestled in the highly sought-after resort-style community of Bellalago. The community is secured with a 24-hour gated entrance for your peace of mind. The home itself boasts a tiled roof and paved driveway and sits on an oversized corner lot. Inside, you'll find a formal living room and dining room for entertaining guests and also a separated room which could be used as a separate suite. A breakfast nook adjoins the kitchen which features ample cupboard space, a central island and stainless steel appliances. The master bedroom offers direct access to the rear screen-enclosed porch, as well as from the family room and nook. The master bathroom includes two walk-in closets, dual sinks, a garden tub and separate shower.  A conveniently located laundry room sits between the kitchen and garage complete with washer and dryer. Bellalago offers an array of community amenities including a basketball court, tennis courts, clubhouse & dock. For families there's also playgrounds & pools complete with a water slide! Fitness enthusiasts will appreciate the state-of-the-art fitness center offering various classes to suit all levels. For pet owners there's even a dog park! And everyone can enjoy strolling along Bellalago's beautiful 1,300-foot boardwalk, perfect for those pleasant walks!
